OL,3,CWhy schools must be the frontline of
OL,4,Cthe struggle against antisemitism
OL,6,FOn my show last night, in the hours
OL,7,Fafter the assaults in Golders Green, I
OL,8,Ftalked to the transport secretary
OL,9,Fabout the under-reported rise of
OL,10,Fantisemitism among young people.
OL,12,FHeidi Alexander made a point of saying
OL,13,Fthat education and the classroom are
OL,14,Fwhere much of the struggle against
OL,15,Fantisemitism must be focused, because
OL,16,Fhatred of and contempt for Jews is
OL,17,Fprevalent in too many communities,
OL,18,Fsocial classes, ethnicities and faiths.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
