OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777572670
OL,3,CWhy schools must be the frontline of
OL,4,Cthe struggle against antisemitism
OL,6,FThe trigger, the proximate cause, is
OL,7,Ffury at Israel's destruction of Gaza,
OL,8,Ffor which Jews - in general - are
OL,9,Foften and wrongly held accountable.
OL,11,FThis notion that Jews should be blamed
OL,12,Ffor the actions of Israel's government
OL,13,Fis totally irrational and hateful. It
OL,14,Fis antisemitism, pure, simple and
OL,15,Fcancerous.
OL,17,FBut like the virus it is, antisemitism
OL,18,Fis manifesting through tropes that are
OL,19,Fnew and centuries old.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
