OL,3,CWhy schools must be the frontline of
OL,4,Cthe struggle against antisemitism
OL,6,FThat's why there is an imperative to
OL,7,Fengage with young people in schools,
OL,8,Fto help them understand why hatred of
OL,9,FJews is so destructive.
OL,11,FThe government has recently launched a
OL,12,Freview of antisemitism in schools,
OL,13,Fchaired by Sir David Bell.
OL,15,FIf you are in doubt that such an
OL,16,Finvestigation is badly needed, read
OL,17,Fbelow what one teacher told me this
OL,18,Fmorning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
