OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777572670
OL,3,CWhy schools must be the frontline of
OL,4,Cthe struggle against antisemitism
OL,6,FThis is just one teacher and one
OL,7,Fschool. But even so, it is profoundly
OL,8,Fshocking. And I do not believe what
OL,9,Fyou will read is anomalous.
OL,11,FI teach at a London secondary school.
OL,12,FThe otherwise kindhearted children,
OL,13,Fempathetic and intelligent, bandy
OL,14,Fcasual antisemitism about the
OL,15,Fclassroom constantly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
