OL,3,CWhy schools must be the frontline of
OL,4,Cthe struggle against antisemitism
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FI had to explain that Weimar Jews did
OL,12,Fnot cause hyperinflation. Even "old
OL,13,Fschool" antisemitism is back, thanks
OL,14,Fto TikTok revisionism.
OL,16,FAnd with great frequency, students
OL,17,Fremark that "Jews control the world"
OL,18,For that "Israel controls America."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
